query.pigql: a = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour', count() as 'sum_TotalCalls', avg('CallDurationInSeconds') as 'avg_CallDurationInSeconds';a = order a by 'time_Hour' asc;

a = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');a = filter a by 'IsCall' == "Yes";a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour',(1 - erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * exp(((((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds')) - unique('Owner.Id')) * ${Constants.IncludeServiceLvl} / avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * 100 as 'Service_Level';a = group a by all; a = foreach a generate avg('Service_Level') as 'service_level'

a = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');a = filter a by 'IsCall' == "Yes";a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour',erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) as 'er_c',erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * 100 as 'Probability_of_Waiting';a = group a by all; a = foreach a generate avg('Probability_of_Waiting') as 'prob_waiting'

a = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');a = filter a by 'IsCall' == "Yes";a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour',erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) as 'er_c',erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * 100 as 'Probability_of_Waiting',(1 - erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * exp(((((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds')) - unique('Owner.Id')) * 50 / avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * 100 as 'Service_Level';a = order a by 'time_Hour' asc;

a = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour',unique('Owner.Id') as 'total_Agents';a = order a by 'time_Hour' asc;

a = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}}; a = group a by 'Owner.Name';a = foreach a generate avg('CallDurationInSeconds') as 'avg_CallDurationInSeconds', unique('Case.Id') as 'sum_CaseId', 'Owner.Name' as 'Owner.Name', count() / unique('Case.Id') as 'avg_Calls_Per_Case';

q = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}";q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}}; q = group q by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');q = foreach q generate 'CreatedDate_Year'+"~~~"+'CreatedDate_Month'+"~~~"+'CreatedDate_Day' as 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day', unique('Id') as 'dailyCalls',avg(unique('Id')) over ([..] partition by all ) as 'avg_dailyCalls',sum(1) over ([..] partition by all) as 'Counter';q = group q by 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day';q = foreach q generate 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day' as 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day', power(first('dailyCalls') - (first('avg_dailyCalls')),2)/first('Counter') as 'sqr_diff_dailyCalls',first('avg_dailyCalls') as 'avg_dailyCalls',first('dailyCalls') as 'dailyCalls';q = group q by 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day';q = foreach q generate 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day' as 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day', first('dailyCalls') as 'total_dailyCalls', first('avg_dailyCalls') as 'avg_dailyCalls',first('avg_dailyCalls') + (3 * sqrt(sum(sum('sqr_diff_dailyCalls')) over ([..] partition by all))) as 'l_UCL',first('avg_dailyCalls') - (3 * sqrt(sum(sum('sqr_diff_dailyCalls')) over ([..] partition by all))) as 'l_LCL';

query.pigql: a = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}"; a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');a = foreach a generate count() / unique('Owner.Name') as 'avg_Call_Per_Agent';a = group a by all;a = foreach a generate avg('avg_Call_Per_Agent')  as 'avg_Call_Per_Agent';

lens_2.query: q = load "${App.EdgeMarts.ServiceActivity.Alias}"; q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('Case.CreatedDate_Year', 'Case.CreatedDate_Month', 'Case.CreatedDate_Day')")}}; q = filter q by 'IsCall' == "Yes"; q = foreach q generate 'CallObject' as 'CallObject','Case.CaseNumber', first('Case.Account.Name') as 'Case.Account.Name', first('Owner.Name') as 'Owner.Name', first('CallDisposition') as 'CallDisposition', first('CallType') as 'CallType', first('Case.Reason') as 'Case.Reason',first('Status') as 'Status',first('Case.${Constants.CaseProduct}') as '${Constants.CaseProductLabel}', avg('CallDurationInSeconds') as 'avg_CallDurationInSeconds'; q = limit q 100;
